title: Micro Mart - 15 August 2013

Micro Mart Magazine for over 19 years, Micro Mart has been the home of low cost computing. It's weekly editorial content covers all aspects of computing, drawing in passionate enthusiasts to its mainstream and niche features. Featuring lively reader interaction and bursting with personalities, it's rounded off with a bustling classified ads section.
